code: public void testSerdeRoundTrip() throws IOException {     BytesStreamOutput bso = new BytesStreamOutput().     TEST_700_REQUEST.writeTo(bso).     byte[] responseBytes = BytesReference.toBytes(bso.bytes()).     StreamInput si = StreamInput.wrap(responseBytes).     GetSettingsRequest deserialized = new GetSettingsRequest(si).     assertEquals(TEST_700_REQUEST, deserialized). }

public void testSerializeBackwardsCompatibility() throws IOException {     BytesStreamOutput bso = new BytesStreamOutput().     bso.setVersion(Version.V_6_2_2).     TEST_700_REQUEST.writeTo(bso).     byte[] responseBytes = BytesReference.toBytes(bso.bytes()).     assertEquals(TEST_622_REQUEST_BYTES, Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(responseBytes)). }

public void testDeserializeBackwardsCompatibility() throws IOException {     StreamInput si = StreamInput.wrap(Base64.getDecoder().decode(TEST_622_REQUEST_BYTES)).     si.setVersion(Version.V_6_2_2).     GetSettingsRequest deserialized = new GetSettingsRequest(si).     assertEquals(TEST_622_REQUEST, deserialized). }
